            <p class="text-lg text-stone leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Huntsville has transformed from the Rocket City into one of America's fastest-growing tech corridors. Cummings Research Park alone houses over 300 companies and 27,000 employees. I help local businesses—from two-person professional firms to growing tech companies—implement AI solutions that save real time and real money.
            </p>

            <a href="/#contact" class="btn-primary inline-flex">
              <span>Book Free Consultation</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Why AI Now Section -->
