              AI doesn't replace your team—it multiplies what they can accomplish.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-3 text-charcoal">Eliminating Repetitive Work</h3>
              <p class="text-stone leading-relaxed">Following up with leads. Scheduling appointments. Data entry between systems. AI handles these automatically while your team tackles work that requires expertise.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
