              <p class="text-stone leading-relaxed">The first company to respond books the meeting 78% of the time. AI-powered follow-up means your leads hear back in minutes—even at 11pm on Saturday.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-8">
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-3 text-charcoal">Expert Work for Experts</h3>
